summary.para: Defines values that indicate the type of sub-channel data.

remarks.para: For details on the format of the sub-channel data, see Sub-Channel Field Formats in the latest release of the MMC specification at ftp://ftp.t10.org/t10/drafts/mmc5.

summary.para: The data contains P and Q sub-channel data.
The data contains corrected and de-interleaved R-W sub-channel data.
The data contains raw P-W sub-channel data that is returned in the order received from the disc surface.
